Data Science Internship Exam¶

As per the directions in the email, I downloaded the three datasets from the provided links. Two of these were in the .mdb format and I made csv copies of these so as to make it easier to import the files. I have utilized pandas and numpy for data extraction and cleaning processes in the following blocks of code.
